<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.2.5">
<l>tīya puntik kañca ṉuṉmēṟ ciṉamu ṭaiyaṉ cōrvu pārttu</l>
<l>māyan taṉṉāl valaippa ṭukkil vāḻa killēṉ vācu tēvā</l>
<l>tāyar vāyccol karumaṅ kaṇṭāy cāṟṟic coṉṉēṉ pōka vēṇṭā</l>
<l>vāyar pāṭik kaṇivi ḷakkē yamarntu vanteṉ mulaiyu ṇāyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If evil minded Kaṃsa who has [great] anger toward you,</l>
<l rend="indent">Seeing weakness,</l>
<l>Catches [you] through deceit,</l>
<l rend="indent">I would not be able to live, O Vāsudeva!</l>
<l>I have spoken to explain that you must regard</l>
<l rend="indent">the words from the mouth of [your] mother.</l>
<l>Jeweled lamp of the herder village, there is no need to go!</l>
<l>Come and stay, drink from my breast!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
